###################################################################
# AnripDdns v6.5.0
#
# Dynamic DNS using DNSPod API
#
# Author: Rehiy, https://github.com/rehiy
#                https://www.rehiy.com/?s=dnspod
#
# Collaborators: https://github.com/rehiy/dnspod-shell/graphs/contributors
#
